&lt;li&gt;5+ years sales experience in medical sales&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operating Room sales experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Orthopedic and/or Medical device experience preferred&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must reside in the territory&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
